data.title: The Prime Minister of Malaysia Abdullah Ahmad Badawi invites Ambassador Christopher LaFleur and Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff U.S. Marine Gen. Peter Pace to take a seat in his office at the be
data.text:
The Prime Minister of Malaysia Abdullah Ahmad Badawi invites Ambassador Christopher LaFleur and Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff U.S. Marine Gen. Peter Pace to take a seat in his office at the beginning of their meeting in Putrajaya, Malaysia, June 4, 2007. The chairman visited Malaysia to help further military to military relations between the United States and Malaysia.
